### Get paged movies
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/movies?page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json


### Create a new movie
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/movies
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "id": -1,
  "title": "Inception",
  "year": 2010,
  "description": "A skilled thief who enters dreams to steal secrets."
}


### Get a movie by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/movies/1
Accept: application/json


### Update a movie
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/movies/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Joker 2",
  "year": 2020,
  "description": "A man that is a joke."
}


### Delete a movie
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/movies/1
Accept: application/json
